00:55:36.469 --> 00:55:42.054
Show me how to lay down my life so that I can take yours up and receive everything that you have for me.

00:55:44.216 --> 00:55:45.778
Okay, and then glory.

00:55:49.762 --> 00:55:55.788
whether you eat or drink or whatever you do, do all for the glory of God.

00:55:55.808 --> 00:55:58.070
1 Corinthians 10, 31.

00:55:59.912 --> 00:56:18.610
Lord, today in everything that I do, every transaction that I make, every conversation that I have, every thought that goes through my mind, the works of my hands, wherever my feet may take me, whether I'm at work or with family and relationship, whatever it is, Lord, I just wanna glorify you.

00:56:22.722 --> 00:56:30.309
Whether I'm cleaning toilets or whether I'm serving the president of the United States, that would be awesome.

00:56:30.329 --> 00:56:32.512
I want to do it all for your glory, Lord.

00:56:32.572 --> 00:56:35.274
Help me to live my life for your glory.

00:56:35.675 --> 00:56:37.917
Help me to shine my light.

00:56:38.017 --> 00:56:39.659
You call me the light of the world, Lord.

00:56:40.019 --> 00:56:41.360
Help me to shine that light today.

00:56:43.843 --> 00:56:45.244
I just want to represent your glory.

00:56:47.206 --> 00:56:51.250
I promise you, if you start every day that way,

00:56:52.738 --> 00:56:55.501
And maybe you already are and you can testify.

00:56:56.322 --> 00:57:10.058
But if this isn't your normal routine, let 2026 be the year that you get on mission for laying down your life for the Almighty Jesus.

00:57:12.000 --> 00:57:18.368
And the full potential that He has for your life, may it come completely true.

00:57:18.448 --> 00:57:20.370
May you bear much fruit.

00:57:21.666 --> 00:57:23.388
Speak this over yourself, guys.

00:57:23.549 --> 00:57:26.993
This is just, this is five of my kind of favorite verses.

00:57:27.053 --> 00:57:38.389
You can apply, I gave it even a little bit different to the youth on Thursday night, but you can apply anything and you can pray any aspect of the word, but this is just some structure.

00:57:39.029 --> 00:57:41.593
We gotta know who we are in Christ, that we're the righteous of God.

00:57:41.613 --> 00:57:47.441
We gotta know that we're empowered, that He came to live and dwell inside of us to give life to our body, our mortal bodies.

00:57:48.102 --> 00:57:48.983
That's encouraging.

00:57:49.023 --> 00:57:50.124
It should be encouraging to us.

00:57:50.184 --> 00:57:51.346
It's not our own effort.

00:57:51.586 --> 00:57:53.168
It's his in us.

00:57:53.989 --> 00:58:03.138
We gotta seek after his will and not our own every single day, because whenever we seek after our own will, we end up getting ourselves in trouble or getting off track with everything that he has for us.

00:58:05.181 --> 00:58:08.304
We gotta have a priority in our life that says, no, kingdom first.

00:58:08.905 --> 00:58:10.466
And that will help us make decisions.

00:58:10.787 --> 00:58:11.708
Do I buy this house?

00:58:12.128 --> 00:58:13.069
Which car do I buy?

00:58:14.411 --> 00:58:15.532
How about this relationship?

00:58:16.213 --> 00:58:19.536
That conversation, do I watch this movie?

00:58:19.897 --> 00:58:21.298
Should I look at that on my phone?

00:58:21.922 --> 00:58:23.384
You know, should I get this subscription?

00:58:23.424 --> 00:58:26.589
Okay, well, how does that line up with the kingdom?

00:58:27.711 --> 00:58:31.156
It helps us to make decisions in every aspect of our life.

00:58:31.176 --> 00:58:33.881
Seek first the kingdom and his righteousness.

00:58:37.586 --> 00:58:50.226
So I pray that we can make this our mission, to have a mission mindset this year and structure our lives so that we can truly

00:58:50.498 --> 00:58:51.920
become more like him this year.

00:58:52.100 --> 00:58:56.366
Then we can look back and say, wow, 2026 was incredible.

00:58:57.188 --> 00:59:04.899
Not because it went so good and everything was so good and I got wealthy and my health was perfect and everything was so great.

00:59:07.522 --> 00:59:14.332
But you don't need all that to work out in order to be smack dab in the middle of the will of God for your life.

00:59:15.013 --> 00:59:18.418
Many of those things will work out when we live our lives for him.

00:59:20.162 --> 00:59:26.430
But I promise you it starts with us daily seeking after him in a structured manner.

00:59:29.755 --> 00:59:31.337
And saying, not my will but yours be done.

00:59:32.539 --> 00:59:33.981
The narrow gate.

00:59:35.643 --> 00:59:38.547
Ask, seek, knock.

00:59:38.567 --> 00:59:42.552
Knowing that he's gonna give you everything that you need.

00:59:43.413 --> 00:59:43.734
Amen?

00:59:45.116 --> 00:59:48.260
All right, so the worship team will come back up.

00:59:48.280 --> 00:59:49.842
We've got one last song.

00:59:51.362 --> 00:59:54.505
All right, and we can close in prayer.

