If you have any questions, guys, if there's anything I said that offended you, talk to Pastor Micah.

01:00:01.973 --> 01:00:02.794
I'm just kidding.

01:00:02.874 --> 01:00:06.218
E-mail Pastor Micah.

01:00:06.238 --> 01:00:07.159
I'll never be up here again.

01:00:09.421 --> 01:00:14.647
If there's anything that was confusing, anything that you just want to get some clarity, clarification on please.

01:00:15.728 --> 01:00:18.591
You can talk with me, you can talk with another pastor here.

01:00:19.632 --> 01:00:21.074
We just want,

01:00:22.594 --> 01:00:24.516
We want the best for you.

01:00:25.197 --> 01:00:33.266
As the family of God here at God's Peak Church, we want this year to be a memorable year, an amazing year.

01:00:33.707 --> 01:00:38.893
The year that you saw the fulfillment of God's will in your life.

01:00:39.153 --> 01:00:46.061
You saw the deliverance from things that have been bothering you and haunting you for God knows how long.

01:00:47.743 --> 01:00:50.386
All that stuff can be remedied and rectified.

01:00:51.138 --> 01:00:54.322
when we seek after him in a diligent way.

01:00:55.964 --> 01:00:58.667
So please, ask, seek, knock.

01:00:58.687 --> 01:00:59.168
Start there.

01:00:59.908 --> 01:01:08.899
Surrender your life fully to him and believe that all things are possible through him who gives us strength.

01:01:08.939 --> 01:01:09.340
Let's pray.

01:01:12.123 --> 01:01:14.906
Lord Jesus, we just thank you for this evening, Lord.

01:01:15.006 --> 01:01:18.130
I pray this message, Lord, was

01:01:20.514 --> 01:01:21.615
from you Holy Spirit.

01:01:22.256 --> 01:01:27.842
I pray that it resonated with each of us just exactly as we needed, Lord.

01:01:27.882 --> 01:01:36.251
That you spoke directly to our hearts, Lord, and not in a condemning way, Lord, but just with great conviction, Lord.

01:01:37.092 --> 01:01:39.254
Shame and condemnation is not kingdom.

01:01:40.936 --> 01:01:41.797
And I thank you for that.

01:01:42.218 --> 01:01:47.624
I pray that none of us leaves here condemned thinking, oh, what a failure, what a loser am I?

01:01:47.824 --> 01:01:49.906
I don't even know if I'm saved, Lord.

01:01:51.010 --> 01:01:54.355
You know us, Lord, and may we know you.

01:01:54.575 --> 01:02:13.183
May we come to you, Lord, tonight and always, Lord, just fully surrendered, fully humbled, laying our lives down for you, Lord, knowing we're forgiven, knowing your grace and mercy are in abundance and full effect in our lives.

01:02:14.565 --> 01:02:20.434
In May 2026, Lord, and especially here in January, may this be the beginning of

01:02:20.898 --> 01:02:22.765
a great transformation of life this year.

01:02:22.825 --> 01:02:25.475
May there be no limit to what's possible in you.

01:02:27.202 --> 01:02:28.125
We lay these things down.

01:02:28.185 --> 01:02:30.333
Jesus' name.

01:02:30.353 --> 01:02:30.514
Amen.
